text:
Bananas in flight,
A clock ticks on the moon's face,
Frogs whisper secrets.

Fish parade downtown,
Elephants juggle moonbeams,
Teapots sing spring songs.

A fridge flies at dawn,
Watermelons sing praises,
Cacti wear top hats.

Frogs tweet, keyboards ribbit,
Lamps shed their light fur in fall,
Socks debating philosophy.

Floating in green tea,
Elephants dance on the moon,
Socks sing melodies.

Rivers flow upstream,
Invisible frogs singing,
Moon dances at noon.
Moon juggles planets, faraway sigh of black holes echoes in solos.

Pickles serenade moons,
Skipping rocks on fluffy bread,
Teapots bloom in June.

Rainbows drench nachos, 
Quantum leap for a tin can,
Opera sung by toads.

Moon whispers to fish,
Carrots levitate in awe,
Dreams knitting the stars.

Bananas skydive, 
Eclipses wearing sunglasses, 
Teapots whisper secrets.

Bananas juggle lamps,
Moon whispers secrets to the sun,
Teapots dream of storms.

Moonlight scoffs at cheese,
Frogs holding tea parties laugh,
Quantum fish blush red.

Moonlit broccoli sings,
Elephants in tutus dance,
Dreams knitting the sky.

Bananas juggle soft snow,
Eagles wear tiny tutus,
Teacups bloom in spring.

Moon waltzes with spoon,
A silent disco in June,
Pineapples maroon.

Snails skydive without fear, 
Bananas whisper secrets softly, 
Mountains wear top hats proudly.

Fridge lights crave late night talks,
Mountain peaks swap weary socks,
Dessert whispers fork secrets.
Dawn's light, saucepan bugs float whispering, Office chairs spin, launch dreaming. Rain plays chess, lilies sigh.

Forks lightning zigzagged toast,
Pancakes fly, world spins syrup,
Moon dips crackers in tea.

Rainbows knitting socks,
Kitchen sinks sing operas,
Cats debate the moon.
Bananas fly high, Sunscreen fills the ocean blue, Snails speed skate on tea.

Flying fishes sing tunes,
Cheese moons in polka-dot skies,
Mountains sip morning dew.

Frogs whisper to cheese,
Mountains don snorkels and flippers,
Moon juggles fireflies.

Pink elephants skate, 
On thin spaghetti highways, 
Fish applaud from trees.

Frogs in monocles debate,
Lunar cheese, soft etiquette,
Rainbows taste of chocolate.

Coffee swims upstream, 
Furniture sings in the dark, 
Pancakes orbit moons.

Sofas swim in tea,
Grass whispers loud secrets,
Cats debate the moon.
